{"tid":462943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲紐西蘭宣布：大麻食品下周起全面合法化","createTime":"2017-11-09T04:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T07:54:02.000Z","uid":5866,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"95b7cbb22684fd46dee0fb9e96ba38147d115eb0","tid":462943,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171108/1048281.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171108%2F1048281.htm&d=jSwC3uiGN3vC7JBO22xqb5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=bd3aa26a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171108/1048281.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「澳洲新聞網」報導，從11月12日起，大麻食品在澳洲和紐西蘭正式合法化， 澳洲人以後可以在超市、零售商店購買到各種含有大麻成分的食品，當中包括大麻麥片、大麻冰淇淋、大麻鬆餅、大麻奶昔以及大麻甜點等。</span><br />\n<br />\n直到2017年4月，他們才開始認為：四氫大麻酚(THC)含量低的大麻種子是可以安全食用。 據瞭解，大麻中主要導致人上癮的物質是四氫大麻酚，這也是大麻產生致幻作用的化學成分。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲大麻食品企業的首席執行官伯納姆表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">大麻種子富含豐富的健康脂肪、蛋白質和各種礦物質。另外，它也可以為許多食物增添美味和營養。</span>澳洲大麻食品生產商愛麗茲和卡米洛表示，大麻種子將進軍澳洲健康食品市場。 據報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">大麻種子的健康屬性非常高，同時也可能是為數不多名副其實的超級食品之一。</span><br />\n<br />\n大麻種子不僅是食品的來源，並且是一種農作物。大麻種子將會出現在咖啡館的菜單上、冰沙中、鬆餅中、餅乾中以及素食食品中，但這些大麻種子不是有導致幻覺 作用的那種。 <span style=\"color: red;\">伯納姆表示，大麻有許多健康益處，它是澳洲紐西蘭食品標準機構承認的一種高營養的食物。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464b41c779d16dc4c6bdcc2360d99e656c1f6664","tid":462943,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e8028d0dadeca702f0b1243c4e508f6527e3b5","tid":462943,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"班道友可以飲下火麻仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de72d69ca04dd4fffa52c9953e3ea60a70004ca1","tid":462943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:54:13.000Z","msg":"「澳洲新聞網」係咪「日本新聞網」d friend?"},{"pid":"52aacad06b4e1f5a86f48a5ad2e1301f05b2226b","tid":462943,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"大麻子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cea46d8504fef5ef5a7aa031ef94b3f7e43a132","tid":462943,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"Poppy Seed 唔係一直都合法架咩 .. 我以前做 Muffin 都落"},{"pid":"4a5b7671d8ecbd58ec439e66e9430e9ed5dff9ba","tid":462943,"uid":21480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f779e05c7298f3566adda5884bf4e0506c9420cd","tid":462943,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係火麻仁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，英文叫 Hemp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2294b099c73feaadd43c21ae8dc8d7e65a3f998b","tid":462943,"uid":128568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪唔識分大麻子同大麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaed2fd4106476f3d2a8c265b96d1fd7b5303b5","tid":462943,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"大麻子唔係一向好多面包都有落咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119281309c75a85437de18e9b19431f2915113ea","tid":462943,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171108/1048281.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171108%2F1048281.htm&d=jSwC3uiGN3vC7JBO22xqb5WU